* [https://github.com/yorikvanhavre/FreeCAD-NativeIFC NativeIFC] has also been merged into the new BIM workbench. With NativeIFC, you can now work on IFC files in FreeCAD natively, with no more translation to and from the FreeCAD file format. Read more on the [[NativeIFC|NativeIFC]] page. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/13783 Pull request #13783]
