* [[IfcOpenShell|IfcOpenShell]], another piece of open-source software needed to work with IFC files in FreeCAD, is now bundled in all official installer packages offered by the FreeCAD team. If you get FreeCAD from a third-party provider, such as your Linux distribution, where IfcOpenShell has not made it yet as an official package, the BIM workbench offers a utility tool to download and install IfcOpenShell. And if you have no use for IFC, the BIM workbench still works 100% without IfcOpenShell.
